LIBRARY STATUS
==============


UNDER DEVELOPMENT
-----------------
The library is barely usable at this point in time. The implementation of DOT Operations are at 20%.
So, if you plan to use this library don't use the DOT operations at this point in time.
Right now only parse_line function is done. It cannot parse a DOT file at this point in time.
Right now only DEBUG build has been tested.
